        <div class="msgSubject">How to maximize SP gain as a THM</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-17 04:05:12 | Edited: Nov 19 2010  1:40am  | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-128998831245921817" id="quote-128998831245921817" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-128998831245921817" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=179&amp;mid=128998831245921817&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=128998831245921817&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_128998831245921817" onclick="followToggle('add','128998831245921817')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
